00:30:25.940 --> 00:30:27.920 align:middle line:90%
you to be very adventurous.

00:30:27.920 --> 00:30:30.290 align:middle line:90%
It saves you money.

00:30:30.290 --> 00:30:31.830 align:middle line:90%
It's all of the above.

