00:33:02.478 --> 00:33:04.840 align:middle line:90%
OK, check it out you guys.

00:33:04.840 --> 00:33:07.260 align:middle line:90%
There's the van.

00:33:07.260 --> 00:33:10.920 align:middle line:84%
And we're going to
walk right over here.

00:33:10.920 --> 00:33:15.260 align:middle line:84%
Doo, doo doo, doo doo,
doo doo, doo doo, doo doo.

00:33:15.260 --> 00:33:19.200 align:middle line:90%
And there's a nice little river.

00:33:19.200 --> 00:33:22.570 align:middle line:90%
But when you feel it it's hot.

00:33:22.570 --> 00:33:25.800 align:middle line:90%
It's a hot spring river.

00:33:25.800 --> 00:33:27.370 align:middle line:90%
There's the van.

00:33:27.370 --> 00:33:29.990 align:middle line:90%
Here's our camp site.

